  "body": "<center>\n  <img alt=\"Rupees logo\" src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/tRZwqnTb/rupees.png\"\n  width=\"500\" />\n\n## \n\n<p float=\"left\">\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/Zwaluw\">\n  <img alt=\"modrinth\" img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/9FYGDrHr/modrinth.png\" />\n  <a href=\"https://www.planetminecraft.com/member/zwaluw/\">\n  <img alt=\"planetminecraft\" img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/XJBfqLnb/pmc.png\" /> \n  <a href=\"https://curseforge.com/members/zwaluw/projects\">\n  <img alt=\"curseforge\" img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/yNr8dPhm/curseforge.png\" />\n  <a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/zwaluwnl\">\n  <img alt=\"ko-fi\" img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/pdcGXBZt/ko-fi.png\" />\n  <a href=\"https://discord.gg/fV9aby4XGG\">\n  <img alt=\"discord\" img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/zBvhMjyh/discord.png\" />\n  <a href=\"https://x.com/realzwuwu\">\n  <img alt=\"twitter\" img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/Z5JxH6x8/x.png\" />\n  </a>\n</p>\n\n## \n\n\nHya!\n\nThis data pack adds rupees from The Legend of Zelda to the game. They can be obtained by breaking grass. Other than that, they're just retextured emeralds, so they can be used for trading. Perfect for your Zelda related projects!\n\nTo make the rupee actually look like a rupee and not like an emerald, put this pack in your resource packs folder as well and enable it.",
